The opportunity for market recovery has existed in all previous market events and pullbacks. Although no one is ever able to predict when a downturn will reverse, staying the course and allowing investments time to overcome these downturns has been the winning strategy. Investors need to build investment portfolios that will allow healthy returns into market recovery, yet be correctly diversified in times of instability. In this recording, Simon Brown chats with multi-management and manager selection head at FNB Wealth and Investments, Carla de Waal. This discussion took place at the Better Investor Conference in June 2022. Watch more sessions here. Brought to you by FNB Wealth and Investments. Moneyweb does not endorse any product or service being advertised in sponsored articles on our platform.